item.content:encoded:
Summer is here, and the hot weather is unbearable! There is no doubt that everyone hopes that they can spend the whole summer by the sea. Who would refuse white sand beaches and swimming in clear waters? For fashionistas, spending summer by the sea is a great time to wear cute wave dresses, tight shorts and floral tops! The princesses want to become qualified fashionistas, but they need your help. Come and choose suitable summer dresses for the princesses, and finally prepare some beautiful accessories!
Click to play.

item.content:encoded:
Today is Natalia’s father’s birthday. Natalia’s father has to go out to work during the day. Five-year-old Natalia and her mother want to prepare for Father’s Day surprises for their father during this time. Natalia decides to wash his father’s car, and then cook his favorite steak for his father. Natalia’s mother will make a birthday cake. They need to go out to buy some ingredients and tools for car washing, buy birthday gifts for dad by the way, and give gifts to dad at night.
Mouse click or tap to play.

item.content:encoded:
It is Christmas again. Santa Claus is busy giving presents to good children all over the world. But he had a problem, his gifts were scattered on the ice and the road to the outside was cut off. So, would you please use your intelligence to help Santa collect gifts and connect roads for him? Santa and other kids will thank you. Try to use as few steps as possible to solve the problem. When you are stuck. Use a hint.
hold to draw
